attributes.description: ALL JAZZED UP!!! - Our 2021 Honda Jazz 1.5 Elegance CVT is here. This nifty little model has a refreshed exterior which is entirely new and is sleeker than before. The steering wheel has two spokes attached to the centre, automatic climate control, a reverse camera and automatic headlights with daytime-running lights. Safety is taken care of with dual front, side and curtain airbags, electronic stability control, anti-lock brakes and electronic brake-force distribution. A truly lovely interior. Very economical and comfortable to drive as well. Nice to sit in, pleasant to look at, comfortable on the road and with an encouraging sense of quality, this little Jazz will be a great buying option for you. Full Dekra condition report and roadworthy test will be done as well. Please note that the price does not include dealership fees and smash and grab.
